  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To evaluate the effect of a 2-stage approach to the internal jugular vein when performing a
      central venous catheterization compared to the traditional one stage approach on the
      incidence of hematoma formation and success rate.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
